72
00:05:00,540 --> 00:05:06,700
♪My heart adrift,
seeking wings to break free♪

73
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:08,540
Brother.

74
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:13,180
The map of the Lin family's stash

75
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:16,140
was found in the Blood Sacrifice Gang.

76
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:20,620
The killers and scouts
of Blood Sacrifice Gang

77
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:23,620
have been dismissed.

78
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:26,020
Homeless members

79
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:28,340
are recruited by Qi Zeyu.

80
00:05:29,340 --> 00:05:32,060
♪In the galaxy,
I yearn for your presence♪

81
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,100
After Qi Zeyu

82
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,740
knew about the stash,

83
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:36,700
he regretted it.

84
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:38,820
He said

85
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:40,900
I'm not only his goddess and heroine

86
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:42,700
but also a wealthy woman.

87
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:46,660
Brother.

88
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:51,740
If you don't get up and marry me,

89
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:55,100
