into going to England.

90
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:08,300
Brother.

91
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:11,060
You have been in bed
for one whole month.

92
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:15,300
♪Our shared past fades
at the intersection♪

93
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:16,540
Don't you want to wake up

94
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:19,540
